{"tid":463281,"cid":17,"subCid":0,"title":"大種乞衣-香港快運獲續牌5年","createTime":"2017-11-09T10:48:08.000Z","updateTime":"2017-11-09T12:50:33.000Z","uid":65328,"like":1,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":6,"replies":[{"pid":"f619fc3013490a67769d83f773f55d54a7002482","tid":463281,"uid":65328,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-09T10:48:08.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://hk.news.appledaily.com/local/realtime/article/20171109/57438130\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20171109%2F57438130&d=qFMizAWkK58qCn8pkwBdHf1gJfeR7%2BEkjjir5NquRfg%3D&h=d459ef62\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20171109%2F57438130&h=18d9934f\" target=\"_blank\">https://hk.news.appledaily.com/local/realtime/article/20171109/57438130</a><br />\n<br />\n香港快運在上月初黃金周長假期間突然取消18班航機，對旅客造成大混亂，但無礙續牌。民航處表示接納香港快運提交的報告，認為快運已採取合理及有建設性的措施，空運牌照局同意將快運現時的牌照在今年11月11日屆滿後，批准再續牌5年。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n班大種乞衣成日話&quot;點解唔可以照買快運， 佢做錯我地班大種乞衣夠團結可以屌柒佢？&quot;<br />\n<br />\n俾人改期/取消/嚴重delay,  慢慢屌， 反正快運無損失， 損失永遠只係班大種乞衣"},{"pid":"e4ac2015cf94bafc3994196e79e4cc0122b4cd5f","tid":463281,"uid":64345,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-09T12:03:12.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><a href=\"https://hk.news.appledaily.com/local/realtime/article/20171109/57438130\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20171109%2F57438130&d=qFMizAWkK58qCn8pkwBdHf1gJfeR7%2BEkjjir5NquRfg%3D&h=d459ef62\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20171109%2F57438130&h=18d9934f\" target=\"_blank\">https://hk.news.appledaily.com/local/realtime/article/20171109/57438130</a><br />\n<br />\n香港快運在上月初黃金周長假期間突然取消18班航機，對旅客造成大混亂，但無礙續牌。民航處表示接納香港快運提交的報告，認為快運已採取合理及有建設性的措施，空運牌照局同意將快運現時的牌照在今年11月11日屆滿後，批准再續牌5年。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n班